1. *Čekamo* da vidimo izdavanje novog filma. (We are waiting to see the release of the new movie.)
2. *Čekamo* još jedan dan. (We are waiting one more day.)
3. *Čekamo* da se vratimo kući. (We are waiting to get back home.)
4. Oni su *čekali* da vidimo šta će se desiti. (They have been waiting to see what will happen.)
5. Mi smo *čekali* da se završi posao. (We have been waiting for the job to be finished.)